  "title": "LocaleLib",
  "description": "Show translated names of items, entities & more in client's language",
  "body": "<center><i>This library is for developers! Do not install on your server unless another resource has instructed you to do so.</i>\n<p>\n\n![Before](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/17fa9e75beb203a127ab9c8e777c5e067bc404c5.png)![After](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/14b01835cbfdd0429a5fdf4922216f4cbbc70f36.png)\n\nSend messages to players with any Bukkit Material, EntityType, or Enchantment for translation into the target client's language. From Afrikaans and Albanian, to Welsh and Yoruba - tearing down the language barrier has never been simpler!\n\n![Chart](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/adeb38ffc09d6fe76c938657efa650c65cf4db60.png)\n\nFor usage guide and examples, [visit the wiki](https://github.com/PikaMug/LocaleLib/wiki)!​\n\nLooking to translate the rest of your text as well? We recommend [Languagy](https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/languagy-1-9-1-15.61663/).​\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a class=\"externalLink\" href=\"https://ci.codemc.org/job/PikaMug/job/LocaleLib/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"bbCodeImage LbImage\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qflOH48.png\" alt=\"[​IMG]\" data-url=\"https://i.imgur.com/qflOH48.png\" /></a> <a class=\"externalLink\" href=\"https://github.com/PikaMug/LocaleLib\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"bbCodeImage LbImage\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1hJqJK7.png\" alt=\"[​IMG]\" data-url=\"https://i.imgur.com/1hJqJK7.png\" /></a> <a class=\"externalLink\" href=\"https://discordapp.com/invite/QdJAv2G7qg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"bbCodeImage LbImage\" src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/506992958894243860/widget.png?style=banner2\" alt=\"[​IMG]\" data-url=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/506992958894243860/widget.png?style=banner2\" /></a>​</span></div></center>",
